3ba8aa749b87a0aed4185221947ea39b382381ac.query:
SELECT
                id,
                created_at,
                user_id,
                is_active,
                quote_asset_id,
                base_asset_id,
                quote_asset_volume as "quote_asset_volume: Volume",

5faa3a2c6d71384b87569f7cba096cb5ea363652.query:
SELECT
                ROUND(CAST(base_asset_volume/quote_asset_volume AS NUMERIC), CAST($3 AS INTEGER))::float as price,
                SUM(quote_asset_volume_left) as "volume: Volume"
            FROM spot.orders
            WHERE quote_asset_id = $1
            AND base_asset_id = $2
            AND is_active = true
            GROUP BY price
            ORDER BY price
            LIMIT $4
